{{expand}}
[[w:JBoss Seam|Seam]] is a Java application stack, developed by [[w:JBoss (company)|JBoss]], geared primarily towards the development of web applications.  Its primary purpose is to pull together [[w:JavaServer Faces|JavaServer Faces]] and [[w:Enterprise JavaBean|Enterprise JavaBeans 3.0]] by removing all of the "plumbing" code.

